structure.unit: JUVENILE PROCEEDINGS -- COMMITMENT AND CARE OF CHILDREN

law.history: Repealed 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 491, effective January 2, 1978. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 161, sec. 39, effective January 1, 1953.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Conformity of existing probations and pending proceedings concerning juveniles to provisions of KRS 208.010 to 208.540.
